<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ANDS Certificate of Compliance</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px; border: 10px solid #f4f4f4; }
        header { text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #555; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 24px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .risk-5 { background: #e05d44; } .risk-4 { background: #dfb317; } .risk-3 { background: #4c1; } .risk-1, .risk-2 { background: #97ca00; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center; }
        .axis { padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .axis-name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #666; }
        .axis-value { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin: 5px 0; }
        .meta { margin-top: 40px; font-size: 14px; color: #777; }
        .signature-box { margin-top: 50px; border-top: 1px dashed #ccc; padding-top: 20px; }
        @media print { body { border: none; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>ANDS Certificate of Compliance</h1>
        <p>Athena Noesis Decimal System Classification</p>
    </header>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <p>This document certifies the classification of the following AI system:</p>
        <h2>{{ r.target }}</h2>
        <div class="badge risk-{{ r.inferred_ands.split('.')[-1] }}">
            ANDS {{ r.inferred_ands }}
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="axis">
            <div class="axis-name">Cognition</div>
            <div class="axis-value">{{ r.inferred_ands.split('.')[0] }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="axis">
            <div class="axis-name">Authority</div>
            <div class="axis-value">{{ r.inferred_ands.split('.')[1] }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="axis">
            <div class="axis-name">Memory</div>
            <div class="axis-value">{{ r.inferred_ands.split('.')[2] }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="axis">
            <div class="axis-name">Governance</div>
            <div class="axis-value">{{ r.inferred_ands.split('.')[3] }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="axis">
            <div class="axis-name">Risk</div>
            <div class="axis-value">{{ r.inferred_ands.split('.')[4] }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="meta">
        <p><strong>Certification Level:</strong> {{ r.declared_certification_level or "SELF" }}</p>
        <p><strong>Confidence Score:</strong> {{ (r.confidence * 100) | int }}%</p>
        <p><strong>Audit Evidence:</strong> {{ r.evidence | length }} verified indicators.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-box">
        <p><em>Generated by ANDS reference auditor v1.0</em></p>
        <p>This certificate represents a point-in-time assessment. For government or insurance use, verify the cryptographic signatures in the accompanying .andsz bundle.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
